      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone prioritizing utility and value. The exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the roof and a few minor door dings, while the interior has moderate wear on the driver's seat upholstery. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future. It is a solid, honest car for someone who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
