      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and she's been a total dream. I've taken really good care of her, so she's running smoothly and ready for many more miles of adventures! It's the perfect daily driver\u2014super reliable, clean, and honestly just a joy to be behind the wheel. If you're looking for a solid ride that won't let you down, you've found it! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 33500.0,
