    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a well-sorted E92 M3 powered by the S65B40 4.0L V8, a masterpiece of engineering featuring eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M-differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recent suspension refresh, while the hydraulic steering rack provides the tactile feedback modern EPS systems lack. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including the critical rod bearing service and throttle valve actuators. It presents as an honest, mechanically robust driver\u2019s car for the purist seeking a high-revving, naturally aspirated experience.",
